result.title: Hokkaido Girls Are Super Adorable!
result.description:
High school boy Tsubasa moves to Kitami City up in Hokkaido, where he meets a "gal" at a bus stop. The sight of her standing alone against the white snowscape, bare-legged despite the freezing cold, captures his heart. (Source: MANGA Plus)

User rating: 96%
